      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why i bother waking up anymore. everything i spent twenty years building... just gone. one week of news cycles and i'm basically a ghost. nobody wants to look me in the eye. i feel like i died a long time ago and everyone is just waiting for the body to catch up.",
